<h2>All set, {{ enquirer.first_name }}!</h2>

<p>The booking {{ transactable.name }} has been paid by {{ transactable.creator.first_name }}.</p>

{% assign duration = transactable.properties.duration -%}
<p>{{ lister.first_name }} will be your passenger for "{{ transactable.name }}" for {{ duration }} {% if duration == 1 -%}hour{% else -%}hours{% endif -%} starting at {{ transactable.properties.trip_start_time | l: 'short' }} on {{ transactable.properties.trip_start_date | l: 'short' }}.</p>

<p>They will be waiting for you at the above booking starting time at {% if transactable.properties.pickup_location != blank %}<a href="https://www.google.pl/maps/place/{{ transactable.properties.pickup_location }}">{{ transactable.properties.pickup_location }}</a>{% else %}TBD{% endif %}.

<p>Please remember (IMPORTANT):</p>

<ul>
<li>Cost of food/drink, parking/tolls, entry fees or cost of 3rd party services (if relevant) are not included in the booking fee.</li>
<li>If you are running late, please let your passenger know ASAP.</li>
<li>Drop-off location should be within approximately 30 minutes of Sydney CBD or another location agreed upon by passenger.</li>
</ul>

<p>Have a great trip!</p>
